    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Areas in parks or other municipally maintained spaces designated for open-air food preparation and dining. They are commonly furnished with tables, seats, and waste receptacles.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
